title: Meltys Quest v1.03c
description: Meltys Quest is about the journey our protagonist, Princess Meltys takes to restore her kingdom. Meltys is a girl who has fooled around all her life, not giving a hoot about anything but herself. But one day the Grolido Monster Empire invades her country, destroys her home, and kidnaps her three sisters. With no castle and no one else to call for help, Meltys decides,Well, I'll like somehow fix everything!Please warmly watch over Meltys and guide her on this light-hearted, sometimes comical
